data.description: This home is situated in Legend Oaks, a quiet, established and well-maintained gated  community. The landscaping of this home features an attractive front yard with amazing  curb appeal, a level, oversized driveway, and a spacious, wooded backyard which is  level with the home. The backyard also has an elevated gazebo, overlooking the lake  for your enjoyment. There is plenty of space in the two-car garage to park your vehicles  as it has an additional bay area with plenty of storage space and a utility sink.  From the moment you enter the foyer, hardwood floors, large profile baseboards and  accented crown moldings welcome you throughout the main floor. This home also has  an audio distribution system throughout the first floor including the covered, screened-in  deck for your entertainment. The primary suite is on the main level and features a huge  sitting area. The primary bath features a beautiful walk-in separate shower,  jacuzzi/soaking tub, double vanities, a heated towel rack and much more! The large,  custom walk-in closet is well lit and includes a linen closet.  The gourmet kitchen highlights stainless steel appliances, granite counters, a gas  range, double wall ovens, a breakfast bar/ island and is open to a kitchenette space and  the two-story great room w/ fireplace. The formal dining room is just off the two-story  great room and adjacent to the kitchen, which makes entertaining a breeze!  As you ascend the staircase to the second floor, you enter a large bonus loft area which  can serve as a secondary lounge area. The upper level has a huge secondary owner’s  suite with a custom walk-in closet. Making this level complete are three additional  bedrooms with ample closets, two full bathrooms, a laundry room with a utility sink and  a water heater room with custom cabinetry for storage.  The fully finished terrace level features a huge theater with a 120” screen with projector  and dimmable sconces, a butler’s pantry with wine bottle/glass storage, a fully equipped  wet bar with mini fridge, granite counters, a Billiards area, a separate Game Room, a  full exercise room in addition to a bedroom with an attached bathroom. There is also a  storage room on this level. You exit the terrace level into the covered, screened-in patio  perfect for lounging, or you can walk out to the outdoor patio grilling area. This private,  wooded backyard is a unique retreat where you can relax in peace. Additional covered  seating is available under the gazebo, perfect for your morning coffee.  This home is a gem! From the warmly painted wall colors to the upgraded lighting which  brightens up each space, you will feel right at home as soon as you walk through the  door. Whether you seek a private retreat or an entertainer’s delight, this home has it all!  Nearby amenities include Publix, CVS, Starbucks, Chipotle, Arden's Garden and the  UPS Store. Conveniently located only 10 miles west of Hartsfield-Jackson Airport, also  near Camp Creek Marketplace, Wolf Creek Amphitheater/Golf Course, and downtown  Atlanta, this home is close to wherever you want to go.
